START BOT

1. INITIALIZE DISCORD CLIENT
   - Load environment variables (Discord token, channel ID)
   - Set up client and UI button for manual signal checks

2. DEFINE TICKERS
   - SPY, QQQ, TSLA, AAPL, AMZN, etc.

3. ON BOT READY:
   - Announce online status in Discord
   - Attach interactive "Run Signal Check" button

4. SIGNAL CHECK WORKFLOW (auto and manual trigger)
   FOR each ticker IN tickers:
       FETCH 15-minute candle data (1-day history) using yfinance
       CALCULATE:
           - Strat candle types (1, 2, 3) using OHLC logic
           - Reversal or continuation patterns (e.g., 2-1-2, 3-1-2)
       IF valid Strat pattern is detected:
           IDENTIFY signal type (e.g., bullish reversal)
           FETCH nearest option strike and expiry using yfinance
           CONSTRUCT Discord message:
               - Ticker, current price, strat type
               - Option idea: strike, type, expiration
           SEND message to Discord channel

5. SCHEDULER
   - Every 10 minutes, run the signal check function automatically

6. ERROR HANDLING
   - Log issues with data fetch, option lookup, or Discord send

END BOT
